  					<p class="beta-p left">When using in-line skates, a scooter or skateboard, are you a pedestrian? Or are you considered to be using a vehicle?  Generally, the answer is that you are considered to be a pedestrian, which determines where you can use your skates, scooters or skateboard. This section includes tips you can learn to help stay safe while on the move. </p>
