  						<p class="beta-p left">Riding on the road is dangerous for any user so we strongly recommend using rollerblades, skates, scooters or skateboards on the footpath. An even better option is to use facilities such as skate parks – it’s much safer for everyone.</p> 
							<p class="beta-p left">However using your scoot skates and skateboard on the footpath is ok as long as you concider others and take care not to harm or endanger pedestrians.</p>
